title: Casey Mulligan on Cuba
description: Casey Mulligan of the University of Chicago talks with EconTalk host Russ Roberts about life in Cuba. Mulligan, who recently returned from a trip to Cuba, discusses the economy, the standard of living and some of the peculiarities of communist control.
author: webmaster@econlib.org (EconTalk: Russ Roberts)
